{"id":90,"ayahs":[{"number":75,"arabic":"وَمَا لَكُمْ لَا تُقَٰتِلُونَ فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ وَٱلْمُسْتَضْعَفِينَ مِنَ ٱلرِّجَالِ وَٱلنِّسَآءِ وَٱلْوِلْدَٰنِ ٱلَّذِينَ يَقُولُونَ رَبَّنَآ أَخْرِجْنَا مِنْ هَٰذِهِ ٱلْقَرْيَةِ ٱلظَّالِمِ أَهْلُهَا وَٱجْعَل لَّنَا مِن لَّدُنكَ وَلِيًّۭا وَٱجْعَل لَّنَا مِن لَّدُنكَ نَصِيرًا","translation":"And how could you refuse to fight in the cause of God and of the utterly helpless men and women and children who are crying, \"O our Sustainer! Lead us forth [to freedom] out of this land whose people are oppressors, and raise for us, out of Thy grace, a protector, and raise for us, out of Thy grace, one who will bring us succour!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/568.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":62104,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং কি হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62105,"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62106,"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"(যে) না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62107,"position":4,"arabic":"تُقَـٰتِلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা লড়াই করছ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62108,"position":5,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"(মধ্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62109,"position":6,"arabic":"سَبِيلِ","translation":"পথে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62110,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62111,"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُسْتَضْعَفِينَ","translation":"অথচ দুর্বল","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62112,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62113,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلرِّجَالِ","translation":"পুরুষ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_075_010.mp3"